OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Ftowards the northeast will become more
OL,7,Fextensive across eastern and some
OL,8,Fcentral parts of the UK tonight. Also
OL,9,Frather cloudy with patchy rain
OL,10,Fdeveloping across western Scotland.
OL,11,FElsewhere, dry with clear spells and
OL,12,Fsome mist and fog.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FEarly low cloud and any fog
OL,15,Flifting in the east, then warm hazy
OL,16,Fsunshine England and Wales. However,
OL,17,Fcloudier with showers Scotland and
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland, and isolated showers
OL,19,Felsewhere later.
